    //run pwn.js

    //monitor cash, once hits first threshold and hack skill is > 200? buy a round of servers
    //run hivemind.js

    //continue to monitor cash, once hits next threshold and hack skill > next point 
    //delete then rebuy servers

    //also continue to run pwn.js ever 100? hack skill up through the max required for nuking

    //figure out what to do with home server during this - run grow.js?



}